title: Welcome To PSYC480 Blog
text:
Kia ora!
Welcome to PSYC480 (2024) blog.
I am Usman Afzali, the course coordinator and lecturer of the course.
This website contains labs and EEG data processing and analysis instructions for Special Topic: Computational Contemplative-Neuroscience taught at the School of Psychology, Speech and Hearing, University of Canterbury.
